; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 1050-1051
; auto_xact_t posting with null amount and an amount_expr that returns a long
; Also covers xact.cc line 1053 (amount_error for non-simple amount)

= Expenses
    (Budget:Expenses)    (2 + 3)

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Test                  Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
                                (Budget:Expenses)            $50.00       $50.00
end test
